title: James LaBrie Solo Albums MP3
description:
James LaBrie started a band called "Mullmuzzler" and released their first album (Keep it to Yourself) in 1999, then Mullmuzzler 2 in 2001. After these two albums they changed the name from Mullmuzzler to James LaBrie. These are 5 great albums and some of the many side projects of Progressive Metal band Dream Theater.

In my opinion, these albums sound a lot like Dream Theater but more of a radio friendly approach than a progressive setup. I really like these albums and James LaBrie's talent is heard in them. It's very emotional and moving and it has a very unique theme.
